Radio Flyer;;1992;;PG-13;;Drama;;7.0;;Richard Donner,David Mickey Evans;;Lorraine Bracco,John Heard,Adam Baldwin,Elijah Wood,Joseph Mazzello,Ben Johnson,Sean Baca,Robert Munic,Garette Ratliff Henson,Thomas Ian Nicholas,Noah Verduzco,Isaac Ocampo,Kaylan Romero,Abraham Verduzco,T.J. Evans,Victor DiMattia,Adam Hendershott,Daniel Bieber;;A father reminisces about his childhood when he and his younger brother moved to a new town with their mother, her new husband and their dog, Shane. When the younger brother is subjected to physical abuse at the hands of their brutal stepfather, Mike decides to convert their toy trolley, the "Radio Flyer", into a plane to fly him to safety.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0105211/